					<![CDATA[
						 <p>-1</p> <p>the anomaly is fascinating but there’s nothing here to relate to. I kept thinking this was leading somewhere but unless I am missing something, I don’t really see any narrative here.</p> <p>I would love to see this expanded upon, even if just the history of this object or someone’s process trying to understand it&#8230; but as it is, I only see a cool anomaly without much depth.</p> 
				 	]]>
