					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7567967#post-3987665</guid>
				<title>Author Post :clap: :clap: :clap:</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7567967/scp-4916#post-3987665</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 20 Sep 2018 12:20:04 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Rigen</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2826105</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This SCP is inspired in no small part by <em>Stargate</em> (the 1994 movie) and the &quot;<em>Toaru Kagaku no Railgun SS: Liberal Arts City</em>&quot; DVD extra by Kamachi Kazuma.</p> <p>Do you think the Russian Sputnik is really the first artificial satellite? I've been wondering if it's not possible for the older civilization to reach the space. There are all kind of rocket fuels, but one of them is the Ethanol-Oxygen mixture that the ancient civilizations might realistically produce on their own, given stable economy and source of sugar. Of course, material engineering to produce a frame that could survive launch and knowledge of orbital mechanics are harder to come by, but the point is that it's not strictly <em>impossible</em> for them to create such feats.</p> <p>I would like to thank <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3213383&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1537446004" alt="OthellotheCat" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3213383)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" >OthellotheCat</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/countless-skies" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3477314&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1537446004" alt="Countless Skies" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3477314)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/countless-skies" >Countless Skies</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rattles" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4377609&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1537446004" alt="rattles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4377609)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rattles" >rattles</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xilascrowe" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2969291&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1537446004" alt="XilasCrowe" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2969291)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xilascrowe" >XilasCrowe</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-raven" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=174995&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1537446004" alt="The Raven" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=174995)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-raven" >The Raven</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mlister" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3027978&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1537446004" alt="mlister" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3027978)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mlister" >mlister</a></span> and IRC user BestJames for their critique and suggestion regarding grammars, phrasing, and mechanics of the SCP article. I would also thank <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jackalrelated" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3207203&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1537446004" alt="JackalRelated" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3207203)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jackalrelated" >JackalRelated</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1537446004" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" >A Random Day</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=414239&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1537446004" alt="Gabriel Jade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=414239)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" >Gabriel Jade</a></span> for giving their general thought and criticism on the article. Y'all are awesome.</p> <p>Thanks for reading and I hope you enjoy this article!</p> 
